---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About - Happy Hour">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About Happy Hour</h1>

    <p>
      <strong>Happy Hour</strong> is a learning platform for programmers.
      Write articles, tag them with topics you care about, and discover
      what others are learning. The platform recommends related articles
      based on tag similarity.
    </p>

    <h2>How it works</h2>

    <ol>
      <li><strong>Sign in</strong> with your GitHub account</li>
      <li><strong>Write</strong> an article using the built-in markdown editor</li>
      <li><strong>Tag</strong> your article with relevant topics</li>
      <li><strong>Discover</strong> related articles from other learners</li>
      <li><strong>Build</strong> your learning streak by publishing consistently</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Philosophy</h2>

    <blockquote>
      Learn anything at anytime in one hour.
    </blockquote>

    <p>
      It doesn't matter what you learn. It matters that you learn consistently.
      Tag your articles so others can find and learn from your notes.
      Over time, you'll build a personal knowledge base and a habit that compounds.
    </p>

    <h2>Tech Stack</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Frontend</strong>: Astro SSR</li>
      <li><strong>Database</strong>: Cloudflare D1 (SQLite)</li>
      <li><strong>Hosting</strong>: Cloudflare Pages</li>
      <li><strong>Auth</strong>: GitHub OAuth</li>
      <li><strong>Content</strong>: Markdown with tags</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Join</h2>

    <p>
      Sign in with GitHub and start writing. Or contribute on
      <a href="https://github.com/danliustc/happy-hour" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about ol, .about ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
